listings.comment: Khan's team is professional. He is super busy but it's still better to have Zoom meetings with him & his team, otherwise some misunderstanding might happen. After the meeting, things went smoothly. Thanks!

The web app is user-friendly, visually appealing, and functions flawlessly across all devices.

Overall, I couldn’t be happier with the work they did. Their expertise and attention to detail have made a significant impact on the success of my project, and I would not hesitate to work with them again in the future. Highly recommended!
